These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: martial-arts, mystery, horror, disaster, scientific, epic
6 different pets are kept: rat, fish, goat, rabbit, horse, snake
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the owner of the horse is between the person watching epic movies and the owner of the rat##2
5. the owner of the rabbit is between the owner of the horse and the owner of the fish##2
6. the owner of the rat is the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
8. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
9. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Movie-Genre           | martial-arts | mystery | epic | scientific | disaster    | horror  |
| Pet   | snake | fish   | rabbit       | horse        | rat | goat |

