.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: tulip, amaryllis, bellflower, rose, lily, balloon-flower
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: time-travel, fantasy, mystery, spy, satire, family
1. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person who growslily##1
3. the person watching spy movies is between the person who growsrose and the person who growstulip##2
4. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
6. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
7. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
8. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Flower   | amaryllis | balloon-flower | lily | rose | bellflower | tulip  |
| Movie-Genre           | family | satire  | time-travel | fantasy    | spy  | mystery |

