.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
There 6 different types of food: garlic, pumpkin, watermelon, kale, peach, plum
There are 6 different nationalities: malaysian, turkish, russian, argentine, british, french
1. the person eating garlic is on the left of the malaysian##1
2. the person eating kale is the british##1
3. the malaysian is on the left of the argentine##1
4. the malaysian is on the left of the person eating peach##1
5. the person eating watermelon is on the far right##1
6. the person eating peach is between the person eating kale and the malaysian##2
7. the turkish is on the far left##1
8. the russian is on the right of the person eating kale##1
9. the person eating pumpkin is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Food         | pumpkin | garlic | plum      | peach | kale | watermelon      |
| Nationality   | turkish    | french  | malaysian | argentine   | british       | russian |

