.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: zombie, crime, spy, romance, action, disaster
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, old-henry, swisher, cain, oliveros, siglo
1. the swisher-smoker is the person watching romance movies##1
2. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
4. the cain-smoker is the person watching crime movies##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is the vegafina-smoker##1
6. the old-henry-smoker is between the vegafina-smoker and the person watching disaster movies##2
7. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
8. the swisher-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Movie-Genre        | crime    | disaster | spy | zombie | action | romance   |
| Cigar   | cain | oliveros        | old-henry  | vegafina     | siglo  | swisher |

