.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-5::.
House: modern, futuristic, cottage, gothic-revival, wooden, cape-cod
City: hannover, miami, san-francisco, prague, paris, liverpool
1. the modern house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
2. the cottage house is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
4. the futuristic house is between the cottage house and the wooden house##2
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
6. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
7. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
8. the wooden house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |   4    |   5   |    6     |
| House   | modern   | gothic-revival    | cape-cod | cottage | futuristic | wooden   |
| City         | paris | hannover | san-francisco | liverpool | prague  | miami |

