.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
6 different pets are kept: snake, lizard, ferret, rat, hedgehog, frog
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: rowing, soccer, water-polo, baseball, sailing, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the owner of the lizard##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the person who's sport is water-polo is the owner of the frog##1
8. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the rat and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2
9. the owner of the snake is the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Pet    | snake | frog | hedgehog  | rat      | ferret | lizard  |
| Sport   | soccer  | water-polo    | baseball | rowing | sailing | lacrosse |

