1. the person playing monopoly is the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person playing whist is on the left of the canadian##1
3. the canadian is between the indonesian and the colombian##2
4. the colombian is the person playing whist##1
5. the indian is on the left of the colombian##1
6. the indonesian is between the person playing monopoly and the person playing bridge##2
7. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing go##1
8. the nigerian is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
9. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |    6    |
| Nationality       | indian | colombian | canadian | indonesian | egyptian | nigerian |
| Game   | billiard | whist    | bridge  | go    | monopoly    | scrabble    |

