.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: time-travel, fantasy, thriller, mystery, superhero, documentary
The people have 6 different jobs:  engineer, nurse, social-worker, coach, scientist, musician
 1. the person watching documentary movies is the coach##1
 2. the engineer is between the person watching time-travel movies and the musician##2
 3. the nurse is on the far left##1
 4. the coach is the person watching documentary movies##1
 5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the engineer##1
 6. the coach is the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the social-worker is on the right of the coach##1
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 9. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
10. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel   | superhero  | fantasy | mystery | documentary | thriller     |
| Job   | nurse | engineer | musician    | scientist | coach | social-worker |

