.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-11::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: hip-hop, classical, house, pop, disco, techno
There 6 different types of food: blueberry, nectarine, lime, banana, spinach, cabbage
 1. the fan pop is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 2. the fan disco is the person eating spinach##1
 3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating banana##1
 4. the person eating cabbage is on the far right##1
 5. the person eating spinach is between the person eating nectarine and the fan house##2
 6. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
 7. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the fan house##1
 8. the fan pop is the person eating blueberry##1
 9. the fan hip-hop is between the person eating blueberry and the fan classical##2
10. the fan pop is the person eating blueberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
| Music-Genre         | techno   | disco | house       | pop | hip-hop    | classical |
| Food   | nectarine | spinach  | lime | blueberry      | banana | cabbage        |

