.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-12::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: blood-red, lavender, ivory, green, azure, white
There are 6 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, mirinda, juice, sprite, water
 1. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 2. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 3. the person who likes lavender is the person drinking juice##1
 4. the person who likes ivory is between the person who likes green and the person drinking water##2
 5. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking water and the person who likes azure##2
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 7. the person who likes lavender is on the far left##1
 8. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 9. the person drinking water is the person who likes blood-red##1
10. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |         3          |      4      |    5    |      6       |
| Color           | lavender      | green | ivory | blood-red   | white  | azure |
| Beverage   | juice | hot-chocolate  | milk             | water | mirinda | sprite       |

