.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-13::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: scooter, quad-bike, airplane, van, trike, helicopter
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: rugby, snowboarding, surfing, climbing, basketball, skiing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the van##2
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
7. the person who's sport is climbing is the person driving the scooter##1
8. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |  6   |
| Transport          | airplane | quad-bike | scooter | trike    | helicopter | van |
| Sport   | surfing     | skiing | climbing   | snowboarding | rugby | basketball |

