 4. the brazilian is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 5. the person traveling to london is between the brazilian and the person traveling to colone##2
 6. the person traveling to hannover is the german##1
 7. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 8. the argentine is on the right of the german##1
 9. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
10. the person traveling to hannover is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4     |       5        |      6       |
