.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-17::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: may, december, july, august, february, october
There are 6 different favourite colors: apricot, fuchsia, chestnut, ebony, blue, aquamarine
1. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who likes apricot is the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes blue is the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in december##2
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
8. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
9. the person who likes ebony is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |       5       |   6    |
| Birthday   | may | august      | february       | july    | october          | december    |
| Color         | blue  | apricot | aquamarine | fuchsia | chestnut | ebony |

